data.description: *The best of both worlds... old house charm with all the updates! *Two (2) Primary Suites on the 1st Floor *4 Total Bedrooms *3 1/2 Bathrooms *One (1) Acre Lot Zoned Agricultural *NEW Carpet *FRESHLY PAINTED *This historic home was once referred to as Shady Lawn *Low Maintenance Vinyl Siding *Vinyl Replacement Windows *Fenced Front Yard & Portion of the Rear Yard is Fenced, too *Side Screened Porch *2 Front Porches - Freshly Painted, too *1st Floor Primary #1 Offers a Deluxe Primary Bath w/Double Sinks & Shower *Family Room w/Fireplace *Living Room/Dining Room - Great Flex Space For Whatever Your Needs May Be *The Primary Suites are on Opposite Sides of the Home Creating Lots of Privacy *Eat-in Kitchen *Finished Walk-Up Attic That Could Serve as a Rec Room or Conditioned Storage *2 Bedrooms Upstairs with Full Hall Bath That Are Completely Separate From One Another... This is a Great Floor Plan *Large Circular Driveway Provides Ample Parking *1st Floor Laundry w/Conveying Washing & Dryer *Beautiful Rural Setting With Amazing Convenience to Highways, Restaurants, Grocery Store & More!
